{"type": "article", "id": 26093, "title": "磁性组合灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-28T07:10:13Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 52, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702170724EJv9tXOjuG6okU2z.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"medium-insert-active\">这款磁性多功能组合灯由双人设计师组合 Plato Design 出品，名叫 D-TWELVE。通过表面附着的磁贴，你可以将它们自由地组合在一起形成凸显个性的照明系统。当然，哪怕只是将独立的一盏摆放在桌上，也非常吸引眼球。你可以通过 <a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1843649997/d-twelve-lamp-the-modular-magnetic-lighting-system\">Kickstarter </a>了解更多相关信息。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170721lHtaDSJouL2EeYXK.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61323529\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170721dZo8701D2Gvh5l4m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66715758\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170722zkZm1hKFUIox9Eqw.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170723RdouMBQ9hcJIn7Fa.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.43529412\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}